Select      LIO.Tarih, OVI.VeriIslemAdi, LIO.InfoParams, LIO.InfoKayit
From        IT15_LogsITObjects LIO
            Left Outer Join IT15_ObjectsVeriIslemleri OVI On OVI.ITVeriIslemID = LIO.ITVeriIslemID
            Left Outer Join IT15_ObjectsM OM On OM.ITObjectID = LIO.DSITobjectID
            Left Outer Join IT15_ObjectsM OMSP On OMSP.ITObjectID = OVI.SPITObjectID
Where       LIO.InfoID Like '%(PlanMakinaID:14154%'
Order By    LIO.ITObjectsLogID Desc







Select      OVI.VeriIslemAdi, LIO.InfoKayit, LIO.InfoParams, OVI.ITObjectID, OVI.SPITObjectID, LIO.InfoUser, LIO.InfoHostName
From        IT15_LogsITObjects LIO
            Inner Join IT15_ObjectsVeriIslemleri OVI On OVI.ITVeriIslemID = LIO.ITVeriIslemID   --INNER JOIN  IT15_ObjectsM OM On OVI.SPITObjectID = LIO.ITObjectID

Where       LIO.InfoKayit Like '%106613%'
Order By    LIO.ITObjectsLogID Desc
